Picture Clause abbreviated as PIC specifies the data type & amount of storage required for a data item.

Alphabetic:  Characters: A    Meaning: Alphabetic
Numeric:  Characters: 9    Meaning: Digits
Alphanumeric:  Characters: X    Meaning: Any Character
Edited Numberic:  Characters: A    Meaning: Alphabetic
Edited Alphanumeric:  Characters: A    Meaning: Alphabetic



